<div id="symptoms" style="display: none; text-align: center; background-color: peachpuff; margin-top: 10px;">
<div style="font-size: 40px;">
	<li>
	The most common symptoms of Covid-19 clash with those of influenza as well as the common flu, and this is the reason why (if you don't count the controversy around it!) Chinese doctors were at first not able to perceive it as a new disease
</li>
	<li>
		The common symptoms are:
		<br>
		Shortness of Breath
		<br>
		Fever
		<br>
		Sore Throat
		<br>
		Dry cough
		<br>
		Tiredness
		<br>
		among other less confirming ones like diarrhoea, runny nose, et cetera!
		<br><br>
		The most we could do now to let you know all the correct information is to redirect you <a href="https://www.who.int/health-topics/coronavirus#tab=tab_3">here!</a>
	</li>
	
</div>
